### Welcome to the SHIELD alliance's repository.
Welcome to SHIELD! If you're an alliance member, you'd find a lot of resources here, pooled by SHIELD members, on making your gameplay better. If you're new to the alliance, please contact rudimk in Wasat OGame, for further questions.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
